com.lrsus.venusdk

Class VENURange

  • com.lrsus.venusdk.VENURange

  • public class VENURange

    Base service providing BLE ranging to determine whether a phone is near a location. Applications must extend this class and implement appNamespace() and brandId() accordingly to the configuration provided by LRS.

    If within range, this service will request a unique service number for the location and pass it to the VENUCallback enteredVENULocation(). It is the responsibility of the app to determine when to begin broadcasting after receiving the range event and service number.
